---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import StructuredData from '../../components/StructuredData.astro';

const comparisonData = {
  title: 'Zyro vs Mixo AI',
  description: 'Zyro vs Mixo: Which AI website builder is better for beginners? Compare features, pricing, templates, AI capabilities, and real-world performance.',
  date: 'January 2025'
};

const tools = [
  {
    name: 'Zyro',
    score: 7.6,
    ease: 8.5,
    design: 6.5,
    ai: 8.0,
    value: 8.5,
    price: '$3-15/mo',
    strengths: ['AI Writer', 'AI Heatmap', 'Affordable', 'Easy to use'],
    weaknesses: ['Limited templates', 'Basic designs', 'No code export']
  },
  {
    name: 'Mixo',
    score: 8.5,
    ease: 9.0,
    design: 8.5,
    ai: 8.5,
    value: 8.5,
    price: '$9-39/mo',
    strengths: ['Fast generation', 'Great templates', 'AI content', 'SEO features'],
    weaknesses: ['No code export', 'Limited customization', 'Basic e-commerce']
  }
];
---

<Layout title={`${comparisonData.title}: Which is Better?`} description={comparisonData.description}>
  <!-- FAQ Structured Data -->
  <StructuredData
    type="FAQPage"
    data={[
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Is Zyro or Mixo better for beginners?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Mixo is better for most beginners. It generates complete websites in under 60 seconds with better templates and built-in SEO. Zyro is also easy but has more dated designs. Mixo's templates look modern and professional from the start, while Zyro's feel more basic."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Which is cheaper, Zyro or Mixo?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Zyro is cheaper at $3-15/month compared to Mixo's $9-39/month. However, Mixo's base plan includes more features. If budget is your top priority, Zyro wins. If you want better templates and AI features, Mixo is worth the extra cost."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do Zyro or Mixo allow code export?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Neither Zyro nor Mixo offer code export. Both are hosted platforms - your website is tied to their service. If you leave either platform, you'll need to rebuild your site from scratch. For code export, consider Framer, 10Web, or Webflow instead."
        }
      }
    ]}
  />

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-semibold mb-4">COMPARISON</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">{comparisonData.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">{comparisonData.description}</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Quick Answer -->
    <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Quick Answer</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">
        <strong>Mixo wins for most users.</strong> Better templates, faster generation, and more professional results.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">
        <strong>Choose Zyro if:</strong> You're on a tight budget ($3-15/mo) and want unique AI tools (AI Heatmap).
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        <strong>Choose Mixo if:</strong> You want better designs, faster site generation, and built-in SEO features.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Score Comparison -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Score Comparison</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {tools.map(tool => (
          <div class="border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">{tool.name}</h3>
            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-orange-600 mb-4">{tool.score}/10</div>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span>Ease of Use</span>
                <span class="font-semibold">{tool.ease}/10</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span>Design Quality</span>
                <span class="font-semibold">{tool.design}/10</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span>AI Features</span>
                <span class="font-semibold">{tool.ai}/10</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span>Value</span>
                <span class="font-semibold">{tool.value}/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Starting Price</div>
              <div class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">{tool.price}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature Comparison Table -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Feature Comparison</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <th class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left">Feature</th>
              <th class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">Zyro</th>
              <th class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">Mixo</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-medium">Site Generation Speed</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">2 minutes</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50">Under 60 seconds</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-medium">Template Quality</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">Basic</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50">Modern & Professional</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-medium">AI Content Generation</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50">AI Writer</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50">Built-in AI Copy</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-medium">Unique AI Features</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50">AI Heatmap</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">Smart SEO</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-medium">Code Export</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">No</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">No</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-medium">Free Plan</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50">Yes</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50">Yes</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-medium">Starting Price</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50 font-bold">$3/mo</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-center">$9/mo</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Strengths & Weaknesses -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      {tools.map(tool => (
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">{tool.name}</h3>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-700 mb-2">Strengths</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1">
              {tool.strengths.map(s => <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><span class="text-green-500">✓</span><span>{s}</span></li>)}
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-700 mb-2">Weaknesses</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1">
              {tool.weaknesses.map(w => <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><span class="text-red-500">✗</span><span>{w}</span></li>)}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Deep Dive -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">The Key Differences</h2>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Template Quality</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>Mixo wins here.</strong> Mixo's templates look modern, professional, and designed for 2025. They come with good typography, spacing, and visual hierarchy.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Zyro's templates feel dated - like something from 2018. They're functional but not inspiring. If design matters, Mixo is the clear choice.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">AI Features</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>Zyro has unique tools:</strong> AI Writer for content generation and AI Heatmap for layout optimization. The Heatmap is genuinely useful - it predicts where visitors will look.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Mixo has AI content generation too, plus smart SEO features that optimize your site as you build it. Both have solid AI, just different approaches.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Pricing</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>Zyro is significantly cheaper:</strong> Starting at $3/month vs Mixo's $9/month.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          However, Mixo's base plan includes more features. If you're on a tight budget, Zyro wins. If you can afford $9/month, Mixo delivers more value.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- My Experience -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-50 to-cyan-50 border-[3px] border-sky-300 p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">My Experience: The $6/month That Cost $3,400</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Real testing, not theoretical comparison</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">A friend needed a landing page for a consulting offer. Same offer, same copy, tested both platforms.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>Zyro:</strong> Built in 2 minutes. Template looked like 2018. Boxy, generic, felt "cheap." Saved $6/month though.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>Mixo:</strong> Built in 47 seconds. Template looked professional. Clean typography, good spacing, modern aesthetic.</p>
          <div class="bg-sky-100 border-l-[4px] border-sky-500 p-4 my-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-sky-900 font-medium"><strong>90 days later:</strong> Zyro site had 400 visitors, 8 leads (2% conversion). Mixo site had 420 visitors, 15 leads (3.6% conversion).</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">The 7 extra leads from Mixo were worth $1,700 each (her average client value). That's $11,900 in additional revenue.</p>
          <div class="bg-cyan-100 border-l-[4px] border-cyan-500 p-4 my-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-cyan-900 font-medium"><strong>The brutal math:</strong> She saved $6/month with Zyro = $18 over 3 months. Lost $11,900 in revenue. Every dollar saved cost $661 in missed revenue.</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>Then the opposite scenario:</strong> A hobby blogger testing ideas. Zero budget, just needs something functional. Zyro at $3/month was perfect. She didn't care about design - she just needed to publish.</p>
          <div class="bg-blue-100 border-l-[4px] border-blue-500 p-4 my-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-900 font-medium"><strong>The lesson:</strong> If you're selling something professional, Mixo's design quality pays for itself 100x over. If you're on a tight budget and design doesn't matter, Zyro works. Be honest about what "cheap" actually costs you.</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">I've seen this pattern repeatedly. Zyro sites convert 1.5-2%. Mixo sites convert 2.5-4%. For landing pages where conversions = revenue, the design gap is expensive.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">Both offer free trials. Test each with your content.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/reviews/zyro-ai" class="bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg">
          Read Zyro Review →
        </a>
        <a href="/reviews/mixo-ai" class="bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-800 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg">
          Read Mixo Review →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
